data.description: GREAT 3 beds/ 2 baths single-family home, nestled in the middle of the family-oriented Deerwood Estates! Unbeatable location near Ronald Regan Turnpike and Miami Zoo. Walking distance to Walmart Supercenter, Restaurant, LA Fitness, Starbucks and more! The interiors have been completely remodeled. Featuring a beautiful cozy living room, dining and kitchen area with complete appliances, breakfast counter, and cabinetry. Bedrooms are gorgeous with enough space for your furniture. Adjacent to the dining room is an open patio outside, a laundry area, and a fenced backyard which is perfect for outside activities. This property provides the perfect blend of urban accessibility and everyday living!!
